Class ProcessUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.randomnoun.common.ProcessUtil
  • public class ProcessUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for running processes, including timeouts, remote execution, and slightly better exceptions that include more information about process failure.
